  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK625">
<l>aṭukki variṉu maḻivilāṉuṟṟa </l>
<l> viṭukka ṇiṭukkaṭ paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The troubles of that man will be troubled (and disappear) who, however thickly they may come upon him, does not abandon (his purpose).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
